00:43:30.460 --> 00:43:32.950
to you no matter how old you are.

00:43:32.950 --> 00:43:36.530
You think, "oh yeah,
I remember that."

00:43:36.530 --> 00:43:38.940
In fact, some of you might
think, "I still feel that way.

00:43:38.940 --> 00:43:40.240
That is a feeling that I have."

00:43:40.240 --> 00:43:43.270
So I hope that...

00:43:43.270 --> 00:43:44.570
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:43:44.570 --> 00:43:45.870
&gt;&gt; Your welcome.

00:43:45.870 --> 00:43:50.950
&gt;&gt; I've always liked how vivid
