can possibly get away with.

00:44:08.010 --> 00:44:09.310
[ Laughter ]

00:44:09.310 --> 00:44:13.400 position:56%
And that the goal is to make the
reader -that that's one of the kinds

00:44:13.400 --> 00:44:17.690
of work that, at least in
short stories, I feel I'm going

00:44:17.690 --> 00:44:20.870
to shove off onto the reader,
I'm going to put in some detail

00:44:20.870 --> 00:44:24.940
